<refsect1 id="BluetoothChooserButton.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
A button used to select Bluetooth devices which will pop-up a
<link linkend="BluetoothChooser"><type>BluetoothChooser</type></link> widget inside a dialogue when clicked.</para>
<para>
</para>
</refsect1>

